The integrated risk assessment cannot be computed until these dimensions are resolved. A conservative stance and a staged approach are warranted, with a focus on delivering the anomalies list (especially from the Financial Analyst) and resolving tool-output blockers to enable parallel analyses and an eventual integrated risk score.
